Key Match Events: The Sacramento Kings rallied from an 18-point deficit in the first quarter to win 110-100
De'Aaron Fox finished the game with 33 points, six rebounds, six assists and one steal
Domantas Sabonis tallied 17 points, 16 rebounds, seven assists and one steal
Miscellaneous Highlights: Doug Christie, taking over the fired Mike Brown, won his first game as an interim head coach
Others: Without Luka Doncic, Kyrie Irving and Klay Thompson, the Mavericks leaned on Spencer Dinwiddie and P.J. Washington
P.J. Washington scored 19 points in the first half and finished with 28
